---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import "../style/global.css";
const siteTitle = "sponsor theo";
const description = "want to sponsor theo? here's everything you need to know";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://t3.gg/images/twitter.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:creator" content="@t3dotgg" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={siteTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://t3.gg/images/twitter.png" />
    <title>{siteTitle}</title>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />

    <script defer data-domain="astro.t3.gg" src="/js/script.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="h-screen bg-white text-black">
    <main class="">
      <header class="flex flex-col gap-2 px-2 pt-4 md:px-8">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-gray-500 hover:underline"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-4 w-4"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width={2}
              d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
          </svg>
          back
        </a>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold md:text-4xl">
          want to sponsor theo?
        </h1>
        <p>here's everything you need to know</p>
      </header>

      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[800px] flex-col gap-12 px-2">
        <section class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">tldr</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-4 text-lg text-neutral-800">
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">3 million viers per month</span> and
              <span class="font-semibold">300k+ watch hours/month</span> (~2 super
              bowl commercials of viewership)
            </li>
            <li>
              the majority of our audience are <span class="font-semibold"
                >employed software engineers</span
              > with <span class="font-semibold">large incomes</span> and
              <span class="font-semibold">real buying power</span> in their workplace
              > in their workplace
            </li>
            <li>
              average <span class="font-semibold">68,000 views per video</span>
              (for our last 8 vids)
            </li>
            <li>
              the <span class="font-semibold">theo guarantees</span> make sure you're
              getting your money's worth
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="pt-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">real impact</h2>
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-lg text-neutral-700">
                <p>
                  Someday I&apos;ll have to tell you how transformational these
                  ads have been for us. Suffice it to say that, last year I had
                  worries about our Q1 schedule going into the holiday season.
                  But this year the biggest worry is how we will service all the
                  new clients going into 2025. I&apos;d rather have this
                  problem!
                </p>
                <p>
                  We did other ads too in 2024, but the Theo ads by far were the
                  most effective for us. When Justin and I talked about the
                  folks we worked with, it&apos;s clear to both of us that you
                  in particular get it, exactly what we need and are adept at
                  delivering it.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-base">
                  Infinite Red
                </p>
                <img
                  src={"/assets/sponsors/infinite-red.svg"}
                  alt={"IR"}
                  width={96}
                  height={96}
                  class="h-24 w-24 object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-lg text-neutral-700">
                <p>
                  I always know when you guys publish something because we have
                  a slack channel with new signups and it&apos;s getting
                  flooded. ðŸ˜ƒ
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-base">
                  Sevalla
                </p>
                <img
                  src={"/assets/sponsors/sevalla.svg"}
                  alt={"IR"}
                  width={96}
                  height={96}
                  class="h-24 w-24 object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="class pt-8">
          <h2 class="pb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">developer sentiment</h2>
          <p class="pb-2">
            developers are <span class="font-semibold"
              >VERY sensitive to being marketed to</span
            >. we spent the last 2 years refining our advertising process to get
            the best possible sentiment from my audience. proud to say we've
            succeeded.
          </p>

          <p>
            you can take our word for it, or just hear it from the audience
            directly:
          </p>

          <Image
            alt="sponsor comments"
            src={"/assets/sponsors/sponsor-comments.png"}
            width={800}
            height={400}
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="pb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">demographics</h2>

          <p>
            75% of our audience is over 25. here&apos;s a quick dump of our
            demographics for reference:
          </p>

          <Image
            alt="demographics"
            src={"/assets/sponsors/demographics.png"}
            width={800}
            height={700}
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="pb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">the theo guarantees</h2>

          <p class="pb-4 md:text-lg">
            We want to make sure that you get your money's worth from every ad:
          </p>

          <ol class="list-decimal space-y-2 pl-6 text-neutral-900 md:text-lg">
            <li>
              The ad will be at least <span class="font-semibold"
                >45 seconds long</span
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              The ad will be included in the first <span class="font-semibold"
                >2 minutes</span
              > of the video
            </li>
            <li>
              The ad will be placed in a video <span class="font-semibold"
                >relevant to your intended audience</span
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              The ad will be seen at least <span class="font-semibold"
                >35,000 times</span
              > within 30 days of publication
            </li>
          </ol>

          <p class="pt-4 md:text-lg">
            If any of these guarantees aren't met, we'll give you a free ad spot
            to make up for it
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="flex items-center justify-center py-16">
        <p class="text-2xl">
          want to learn more? email us at:
          <span class="font-semibold">youtube@thisdomain</span>
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
